# 📚 Library Management Application (Spring XML-Based Dependency Injection)

This is a basic Java application demonstrating how to use **Spring Framework's Dependency Injection (DI)** using **XML configuration** in a **Library Management System**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Demonstrates **Setter-based Dependency Injection** using Spring.
- Uses **Maven** for build and dependency management.
- Simple modular structure with `Book`, `BookService`, and `BookRepository`.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Java 8+
- Spring Framework (v5.3.x)
- Maven
- Eclipse IDE

---

## 📁 Project Structure

LibraryManagementApp/
├── src/
│ └── com/example/library/
│ ├── Book.java
│ ├── BookRepository.java
│ ├── BookService.java
│ └── LibraryManagementApplication.java
├── applicationContext.xml
├── pom.xml



